702162f-a.title: Bronx: White Plains Road - Penfield Street
702162f-a.text:
White Plains Road, at the S.E. corner of Penfield Street, showing
the Wakefield-Grace (M.E.) Church. On the left, at the N.E. corner,
appears part of a 2-story building of the New York Telephone Co.
May 24, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
